<html>
<head>
<style type="text/css">
.vm-container {
	margin: 10px;
}
.vm-page-content {
	border: 1px solid #2a3f54;
	height: 130%;
	color: #000;
}

.vm-page-content .head {
	background-color: #2a3f54;
	padding: 10px;
	color: #FFFFFF;
}

.head .images {
	margin-left: 10px;
}

.vm-page-content .body {
	padding: 10px;
	font-size: 12px;
}
.resp{
margin: 5px 0px;
}
.resp h5 {
	font-size: 13px;
	font-weight: 600;
}

.body .cont p {
	margin: 0 0 8px;
	text-align: justify;
	line-height: 20px;
}

.sub-title {
	font-size: 13px;
	font-weight: 600;
	line-height: 30px;
}

.sub-mrg-content {
	margin-top: 3px;
	margin-bottom: 3px;
	padding-left: 30px;
}
.sub-mrg-content li{
line-height: 25px;
}
.btn{
padding: 10px;
background:  #2a3f54;
color: #ffffff;
margin: 5px;
text-align: center;
border-radius:3px;
}
.footer {
	padding: 10px;
	background: #fff;
}
.footer-reg{
font-size: 12px;
	color: #000;
	font-weight: 600;
	line-height: 20px;
}
.footer .quas {
	margin-top: 20px;
	font-size: 12px;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
	<div class="vm-container">
		<div class="vm-page-content">
			<div class="head">
				<div class="images">
					<img src="cid:imagess" alt="MyJobKart" />
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="body">
				<div class="resp">
					<h5>Dear ${firstName}  </h5>
				</div>
				<div class="cont">
				<p>Congratulations! Your profile has been created successfully.</p><p> By default, your profile is inactive; please visit your profile page to activate the same. At MyJobKart.com, you can create infinite number of profiles and activate the most relevant one of your choice; in short, MyJobKart.com is dynamic from the user perspective.</p>
				<p>Please login to your account with the following credentials,</p>
					
				<ul class="sub-mrg-content">
					<li><b>User Id :</b> ${emailId}</li>
                    <li><b>PassWord:</b> ${password}</li>				</ul>
                    <p>Myjobkart.com enables you to enrich your career in all the best possible ways by paving a remarkable guidance with the following offers like,</p>
                    
                    <ul class="sub-mrg-content">
                    <li><b>Apply for a Job-</b> You can apply for a job in accordance with your skills, profession and experience.
                    <li><b>Create Job Alert-</b> You can create an alert for a job pertaining to your key skills, location, experience, Job Type and Role.
				<li><b>Employer View History-</b>It is a visibility for you to view the employer who had shown interest in your profile.
                <li><b>Find Jobs-</b> You can best choose a job juxtaposed based on your preferred location, skills/job title and experience.
                <li><b>Manage Following-</b> You can track/ follow your preferred organization’s recruitment.
                <li><b>Save Job-</b> You can save your prioritized jobs for future reference.</li>
			</div>
			<div class="footer">
				<div class="footer-reg">
					Warm Regards<br /> MyJobKart.com
				</div>
				<div class="quas">
					 For more clarifications, ping us at <b>info.myjobkart@gmail.com</b>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</body>
</html>
